<P>
   CALIFORNIA KEEPS THE SLOTS SPINNING
</P>
<P>
   A7916 BC-NOBUSING11-COX 633 20:26 U A
</P>
<P>
   A7914 BC-EXP-CONGRESS-TAX-NYT 462 20:25 U A
</P>
<P>
   USING BUDGET SURPLUS FOR DEBT REDUCTION BECOMING A POLITICAL
OPTION
</P>
<P>
   A7906 BC-EXP-PUERTORICO-CLEMENCY-NYT 503 20:20 U A
</P>
<P>
   11 PUERTO RICAN PRISONERS RENOUNCE TERRORISM AND GO FREE
