asset that could be spread profitably across the company's many
computer divisions. And he streamlined management, slashed
bureaucracy and built up IBM's faster-growing services and software
businesses.
</P>
<P>
   The results have been impressive, as profits and IBM's stock
price have rebounded. The laudatory reviews extend well beyond Wall
