   CLINTON-APEC-$ADV12 _ WASHINGTON _ President Clinton heads to
the two-day APEC Economic Leaders meeting in New Zealand at a
pretty tumultous time in the region _ security concerns abound from
the Indian subcontinent to East, Timor, Indonesia to the Taiwan
Straits to the Korean Peninsula. Developing. (Deans, Cox News
Service). MOVED
</P>
