out of the gate earlier this year. But this fall, with a new team
running the show, Gore is trying to find a new footing. It's
crucial that he does. Democrats are getting jittery that he
continues to trail Texas Gov. George W. Bush, the Republican
frontrunner, by double digits in public opinion polls. (Shepard,
