cigarette company against anti-smoking lawsuits and his current
legal situation, where he is is representing a one-man Internet
newsletter against a lawsuit filed by Ford Motor Co. ``As I look at
it, I keep saying, 'It's like tobacco.' `` says Pickrell, 33.
(Chris Berkey/New York Times Photo)
